{
  "stem": "214.4",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And the man opens the door and looks at us.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And very politely says, what can I do for you.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH] tells him this story.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And he looks at us and he says, well, I would never do it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It would jeopardize my life.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And this, and that, and the other thing.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And then, I know his name.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "His name was George, whatever [NON-ENGLISH] something.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he says-- he looks at me and he says, but I have a suggestion to you.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "You don't look Jewish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "We are desperate to send people to Germany.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We are having a hard time getting them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "They are hiding.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They are giving us all false information, this and that.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "If you want to go to the [NON-ENGLISH] and volunteer, and if nobody will have any suspicion of who you are, they will send you off without anything, and you may save your life.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And that's really how it was.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "And that's another thing.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And [NON-ENGLISH], she didn't want to do it.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "Actually, she was a very beautiful young girl.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "But she had dark hair and brown eyes, or whatever.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But she, again, asks him to-- there was a Polish family in [NON-ENGLISH], which was not far from [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And she thought if she could get-- this was good friends, before the war, of her family, that if she could get to this family, they probably would save her.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "Because it was really, you know, it was getting sort of yes and no late in the war.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "The Poles were suffering a lot also.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "So what she would need is a permit to take the train from [NON-ENGLISH] to [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And he says, yes, this he can do for her.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I come back to the ghetto, and I tell everybody.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
